item.name: CELEBRATION PACKS
item.description: The Celebration Collection consists of more than 1400 items made up of 20% legendary, 55% epic, and 25% rare items. Each item has a 0.07% chance of dropping in packs that contain duplicates. Non-duplicate packs have moving odds depending on your inventory.
item.subtitle: See the complete list [in the PDF file](https://rainbow6.com/celebration_pack_full_list).
